## Polling Pattern (Canlı Veri)

```typescript
// useEffect ile otomatik yenileme
useEffect(() => {
  loadData();  // İlk yükleme
  const interval = setInterval(loadData, 30_000);  // 30 sn
  return () => clearInterval(interval);
}, []);
```

## İstanbul Saati Gösterimi

```typescript
// Tüm tarihler Istanbul timezone'unda gösterilmeli
const formatTime = (iso: string) =>
  new Date(iso).toLocaleString("tr-TR", {
    timeZone: "Europe/Istanbul",
    dateStyle: "short",
    timeStyle: "medium",
  });
```

## Sayfa Yapısı

```
frontend/src/app/
  page.tsx              → Overview (bakiye, pozisyonlar, sistem sağlığı)
  trades/page.tsx       → Simüle işlemler (pagination + live)
  wallets/page.tsx      → Wallet leaderboard + drawer
  markets/page.tsx      → Market monitor + actionability
  signals/page.tsx      → Signal feed (pagination + live)
  analytics/page.tsx    → Equity curve, strategy health, metrics
  research/page.tsx     → Research Lab (experiment, wallet intel, alpha backtest)
  settings/page.tsx     → Risk profili, strategy parametreleri
```

## Pagination Standartı

```typescript
// Trades ve Signals sayfaları için standart pagination
const [page, setPage] = useState(0);  // 0-indexed
const PAGE_SIZE = 50;

// offset = page * PAGE_SIZE
const data = await fetch(`${API}/trades?limit=${PAGE_SIZE}&offset=${page * PAGE_SIZE}&hide_zero_pnl=true`)
  .then(r => r.json());
// Response: { total, limit, offset, strategies, exit_reasons, trades[] }
```

## Trades API Filtreler

```
GET /api/trades?limit=50&offset=0
  &status=open|closed
  &strategy=direct_copy|high_conviction|leader_copy|dislocation
  &exit_reason=market_resolved|stop_loss|target_hit
  &hide_zero_pnl=true   # realized_pnl=0 olan closed pozisyonları gizle
```

## Drawer / Modal Pattern

```typescript
// Wallet detail drawer
const [selected, setSelected] = useState<WalletEntry | null>(null);

// Drawer açık olduğunda alpha + decay fetch
useEffect(() => {
  if (!selected) return;
  fetchAlphaDetail(selected.wallet_id);
  fetchDecayDetail(selected.wallet_id);
}, [selected?.wallet_id]);
```

## Önemli Endpoint Yolları

| Endpoint | Açıklama |
|----------|----------|
| `GET /api/wallets/intelligence/alpha-leaderboard` | Alpha score sıralaması |
| `GET /api/wallets/intelligence/influence-graph` | Leader/follower graph |
| `GET /api/wallets/{id}/alpha` | Tek wallet 6-faktör breakdown |
| `GET /api/wallets/{id}/alpha-decay` | Wallet decay analizi |
| `GET /api/markets/actionability` | Tradeable market listesi |
| `GET /api/analytics/strategy-health` | Strategy rolling metrics |
| `GET /api/analytics/alpha-backtest` | 5-bucket IQ testi |
| `GET /api/analytics/daily-digest` | Günlük özet |
